Run a pipeline configuration file.
pipeline       JSON structure composed of 1 or more stages
   stages      Stages are composed of 1 or more tasks
      tasks    Tasks are single things to run

[File Structure]

   bin/
      flowb                      

   config/
      config.py                  Data structure - Used to resolve flow file based on project,branch,flow

   flows/                        Holds flow files.  Flow files describe stages and their tasks to run.
      verifier.json              JSON structure defining a flow

   tasks/                        Directory of tasks (executable scripts), subdirs are OK
      taskA
      taskB
      foo/taskA
